STATISTICS:

Damage: 1d10 + 3
THAC0: +3
Equiping Bonuses:
  +10% Magic Resistance
  +10% Slashing Resistance
  +10% Piercing Resistance
  +10% Crushing Resistance
  +10% Missile Resistance
  +2 Bonus to all saving throws
