Weight: 10
Speed Factor: 9
Proficiency Type: Axe
Type: Two-Handed
Requires: 10 Strength~
@650008 = ~This two handed sword is quite a prize.  It is an enchanted weapon, awarding a +3 to hit and to damage.  Aside from the sharpness and balance of the weapon, the sword also confers magical bonuses to the user.  Anyone equiping Furcolo gains a 35% bonus to their magic resistance, as well as being completely immune to undead beings.  The sword is an intelligent entity, and can cast Absolute Immunity upon it's weilder once per day.

STATISTICS:

