@650262 = ~This gruesome collection of human and demi-human scalps sewn onto a heavy fabric makes any warrior, thief, or other class an imposing figure.  While it does not award any special bonuses to the wearer, it will make the person who wears this cloak less likable to others, as appearance of a figure makes a lasting impression.

