@650513 = ~A number of these shields can be found in Waukeen's temples throughout Faer√ªn.  The Church crafts these shields to sell to enterprising adventurers.  In exchange for the powers of the device, the bearer is required to keep the front of the shield uncovered and in its original state.  If the owner does not comply, the shield's powers fail.  In this way, dozens of adventurers walk the Realms bearing the golden face of Waukeen on their arm.

