@650515 = ~The only material parts of this icy weapon are the hilt, grip, and pommel, wrought from shining silver and steel.  It was created in 1099 DR by the chosen of Auril, Ihanora the Merciful.  Ihanora roamed the north, leading ruthless attacks against all those who attempted to find solace from the cold or fight its effects.  She traveled with a motley crew of yetis, polar worms, frost giants, and a white dragon, freezing everything in her wake.  Ihanora was defeated in 1108 by the notorious Red Mask Brigade, headed by the ruthless killer known as Bitter Harley.

