This sword is truly a weapon worthy the finest fighting skills, as it allows the weilder to cut through the defenses of most other creatures.  Upon a successful hit against a target of 18th level of less, the creature is instantly killed when struck, an ability which can be quite useful when forced to fight powerful enemies.


