@650621 = ~The typical dagger has a pointed, double-edged blade, as opposed to a knife which has a single edge and is a bit shorter.  This particular dagger is magical, having special bonuses to its speed, accuracy, and damage it causes.  Also, since it is magical, is it capable of striking opponents that are immune to normal weapons, such as vampires, elementals and mummies.

