@650631 = ~This robe, commonly worn by Cowled Wizards, bestow a number of enchantments upon the wearer.  In addition to lowering the armor class to 4, it awards a 25% bonus to the following damage types:  Fire, Cold, Acid, Electrical, and Magic.  Many young Cowled Wizards receive it as a gift from their instructors upon successfully completing their first five years of an apprenticeship. As with other such robes, they can only be worn by those of the wizardly profession.

