@650644 = ~Helm of Thieving
Mat Savasta, one of the most talented burglars on the Sword Coast, wore this helm on many of his scores.  The helm, a simple leather coif, enhanced Mat's already impressive lock picking abilities.  In the cities of Waterdeep, Luskan, Neverwinter, Baldur's Gate, Athkatla, or Calimport, there wasn't a door that could not be unlocked by Mat.  To activate the helm, the proper command word must be known at which point a burst of energy magically shapes itself into that of a key that closely fits the lock.

