  Grants wearer Infravision~
@650646 = ~The hatchet is a simple tool which can, in a pinch, be used as a weapon to those desperate enough.  The axe blade has a sharp steel blade, capable of cutting wood or flesh alike.  The short handle has a point of the bottom and the head may have a spike on the top.

