@661022 = ~Tempus, known as the Lord of Battles, is the warriors god, and turns his favor from one group of warriors to another as a war progressess.  He rewards the brave and valiant, and many fighters swear by him.  This large shield has been emblazoned with Tempus' holy symbol: a blazing sword on a blood-red field.  It awards whomever uses the heavy steel shield with various bonuses useful in battle.

